---
title: Creamy Mushroom Stroganoff & Garlicky Greens with Potato Mash
description: You'll want to make sure you have this Russian-inspired fav all to yourself. We've kept the key elements of mushrooms, veggies
and creamy sauce, but we've added tomato paste for extra flavour. Finish it with a fluffy mash to soak up the extra sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6719a605d97e45ff0e200e4a-507c8d0e.jpeg
